# APA Loop

```!
bash scripts/apa-loop-setup.sh $ARGUMENTS
```

Please work on the task. When you try to exit, the apa-loop Stop hook feeds back a fresh prompt built from `skills/apa-loop/SKILL.md` and `docs/IMPLEMENTATION_STATUS.md`.

CRITICAL: Only output `<promise>COMPLETE</promise>` when the Completion Gate in `skills/apa-loop/SKILL.md` is genuinely and completely met. Do not output it to escape the loop.
